 1 - (Room TSO8).<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;\">Filtered Lysis Buffer:  <\/span><span style = \"font-style:italic;\">filter lysis buffer using sterile syringe and filter.<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-style:italic;\">Sterile filter and syringe are in closet 1 (Room PSO3).<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">Prymo siringe filter<\/span><span>: catalog number EPSPE2230 Euroclone, Italy.<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>Storage: <\/span><a href=\"#\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\"> <\/span><\/a><span>  Fridge 2 - (Room PSO3).<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">NH<\/span><span style = \"font-weight:bold;vertical-align:sub;\">4<\/span><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">Cl: <\/span><span>catalog number 1.01145.1000 Merck, Italy.<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">KHCO<\/span><span style = \"font-weight:bold;vertical-align:sub;\">3<\/span><span style = \"font-weight:bold;vertical-align:sub;\">:<\/span><span>catalog number 1.04854.500 Merck, Italy.<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">EDTA: <\/span><span>catalog number ED2SS Sigma, Italy.<\/span><\/div><\/div>","materials":[],"description":null,"changed_on":1588083650}